story*

Once up on a time , in a forest there lived a monkey who resided on a plum tree which was on the banks of a river
In the same forest there lived a crocodile and his wife.....
on day the crocodile came to the banks of the river and waited under the treethe kind hearted monkey offered him some fruits
the crocodile came back the next dayfor more fruits
As he loved them . As days pass by , the crocodile and the monkey became good friends 
 